title: NLSModel Experiments
---

```{julia}
using NLPModels
```

```{julia}
struct NLSModel{T, S} <: AbstractNLPModel{T,S}
  A::Matrix{T}
  b::Vector{T}
  meta::NLPModelMeta{T, S}
  counters::Counters
end
```

```{julia}
m, n = 2, 3
A = rand(m, n)
b = rand(m)
nls = NLSModel(A, b, NLPModelMeta(n), Counters())
```
